    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of common Eurasian thrush; the male has black plumage and a yellow bill and is noted for its melodious song, and the female is dark brown.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
